  "page": "Sarhoy",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #DEDEE2;\">Sarhoy</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\nCity ruins</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Location</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a>, on the <a href=\"/index.php/Rhoyne\" title=\"Rhoyne\">Rhoyne</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Destroyed</th><td>\nDuring the <a href=\"/index.php/Second_Spice_War\" title=\"Second Spice War\">Second Spice War</a>.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Free_Cities.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Sarhoy is located in Free Cities\"><img alt=\"Sarhoy is located in Free Cities\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a3/Free_Cities.png/300px-Free_Cities.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"417\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a3/Free_Cities.png/450px-Free_Cities.png 1.5x, /images/a/a3/Free_Cities.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 94.4%; left: 77.8%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -4px; top: -4px; width: 8px; font-size: 8px; z-index:100;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/8px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Sarhoy\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/12px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/16px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:&#160;%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: -6.5em; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\">Sarhoy</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">Western <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a> and the location of Sarhoy\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><b>Sarhoy</b> is a ruined city in <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a> at one of the four mouths of the <a href=\"/index.php/Rhoyne\" title=\"Rhoyne\">Rhoyne</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_ancient_history:_ten_thousand_ships.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_ancient_history:_ten_thousand_ships.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> It was destroyed by the <a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\">Volantenes</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_Freehold\" title=\"Valyrian Freehold\">Valyrian Freehold</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sarhoy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The <a href=\"/index.php/Rhoynar\" title=\"Rhoynar\">Rhoynar</a> built Sarhoy as a great port city made of pink stone with canals and saltwater gardens. During the <a href=\"/index.php/Second_Spice_War\" title=\"Second Spice War\">Second Spice War</a>, three <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonlords\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dragonlords\">dragonlords</a> and men from <a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\">Volantis</a> sacked the city. The city's warriors were slaughtered and its children sold into <a href=\"/index.php/Slavery\" title=\"Slavery\">slavery</a>. The Volantenes burned the city and salted the earth. After further defeats, Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Nymeria\" title=\"Nymeria\">Nymeria</a> led her <a href=\"/index.php/Ten_thousand_ships\" title=\"Ten thousand ships\">ten thousand ships</a> down the <a href=\"/index.php/Rhoyne\" title=\"Rhoyne\">Rhoyne</a> past Sarhoy and into the <a href=\"/index.php/Summer_Sea\" title=\"Summer Sea\">Summer Sea</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_ancient_history:_ten_thousand_ships.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_ancient_history:_ten_thousand_ships.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>According to Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Yandel\" title=\"Yandel\">Yandel</a>, Sarhoy \"remains in ruins to this day, a desolate and haunted place.\"<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_free_cities:_volantis.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_free_cities:_volantis.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sarhoy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_ancient_history:_ten_thousand_ships.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_ancient_history:_ten_thousand_ships.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_ancient_history:_ten_thousand_ships.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Ancient History: Ten Thousand Ships.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_free_cities:_volantis.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_free_cities:_volantis.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\"